children.name: TextMeshPro
children.characters: Welcome to the Spatia-list Post-it notes! Your virtual post-it notes. Click next to proceed.

children.name: TextMeshPro
children.characters: Now, you need walk around the room that you want to map. Try to look at the different parts of the room while walking. It will provide a complete feature mapping. If you dont look everywhere, the map can contain some missing parts and we dont want it.

children.name: TextMeshPro
children.characters: Are you sure to cancel the mapping process?
